snippet.title: Warzone 2.0 Launch Trailer | Call of Duty: Warzone 2.0
snippet.description:
Call of Duty #Warzone2 is almost here and it's FREE as a 🦅

Experience the massive Battle Royale, the all-new DMZ mode, and so much more on November 16 🔥 http://bit.ly/PlayWarzone2
